      "role": "user",
      "content": "wait, what? sorry, i think i misread that. what do you mean by \"rogue goblin\"? just stick to the math for me please, i'm just trying to present this to my manager and we don't need the distractions. \n\ncan you just show me the specific formula for adjusting the COGS versus the average inventory so i can compare the two approaches?",
